<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EEC) No 2531/77 of 17 November 1977 amending Regulation (EEC) No 1594/70 as regards the acidification of certain wines and wine products </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI m&auml;&auml;rus (EM&Uuml;) nr 2531/77, millega muudetakse m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1594/70 seoses teatavate veinide ja veinitoodete hapestamisega 17. november 1977 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 816/70 of 28 April 1970 laying down additional provisions for the common organization of the market in wine (1), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 2211/77 (2), and in particular Article 20 (4) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 28. aprilli 1970. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 816/70, millega n&auml;hakse ette veinituru &uuml;hist korraldust k&auml;sitlevad lisas&auml;tted, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 2211/77, (2) eriti selle artikli 20 l&otilde;iget 4, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Regulation (EEC) No 2211/77 amended Regulation (EEC) No 816/70 to the effect that in exceptional years and under certain conditions additional acidification of basic products, certain table wines and quality wines psr may be authorized; whereas, consequently, in order to enable this new practice to be monitored, and pending measures governing oenological practices and treatments, Commission Regulation (EEC) No 1594/70 of 5 August 1970 on the notification, carrying out and control of the processes of enriching, acidifying and deacidifying wine (3), should be amended accordingly; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 2211/77 muudetakse m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 816/70 nii, et erandlikel aastatel ja teatavatel tingimustel lubatakse p&otilde;hitooteid, teatavaid lauaveine ja mpv-kvaliteetveine t&auml;iendavalt hapestada; k&otilde;nealuse uue korra j&auml;lgimise v&otilde;imaldamiseks ja kuni veinivalmistamistavasid ja -viise k&auml;sitlevate meetmete v&otilde;tmiseni tuleks komisjoni 5. augusti 1970. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1594/70 (veini rikastamise, hapestamise ja happesuse v&auml;hendamise menetlustest teatamise, nende l&auml;biviimise ja kontrollimise kohta (3)) vastavalt muuta; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for Wine, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las veinituru korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> The first subparagraph of Article 4 (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 1594/70 is hereby amended to read as follows: </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1594/70 artikli 4 l&otilde;ike 1 esimest l&otilde;iku muudetakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise> "1. </inglise>
<eesti> "1. </eesti>
<inglise> Acidification of the products mentioned in Article 20 (1) and (2) of Regulation (EEC) No 816/70 may be carried out with tartaric acid only. " </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 816/70 artikli 20 l&otilde;igetes 1 ja 2 nimetatud tooteid v&otilde;ib hapestada ainult viinhappe abil." </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas avaldamisele j&auml;rgneval p&auml;eval. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 17 November 1977. </inglise>
